headline.main: Suspected Jihadists Attack Mali Military Position; 12 Dead
headline.print_headline: Suspected Jihadists Attack Mali Military Position; 12 Dead

lead_paragraph: Suspected jihadists from Burkina Faso have attacked a Malian military post across the border, killing at least a dozen Malian soldiers.
